"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-news-josh-tarling-aims-to-combine-road-and-track-at-paris-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Briton to stay in Australia for Adelaide World Cup with Ineos teammates Ganna and Viviani  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6875102945139996, \"rank\": 0.38407266234617327, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 63, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now subscribed  Your newsletter sign-up was successful  Josh Tarlingdoesn't have to look far for inspiration as he bids to race on road and track at theParis 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.6490003573436446, \"rank\": 0.5408310924994526, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The template has already been sketched out by an Ineos Grenadiers teammate, after all.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo three years ago,Filippo Gannapowered Italy to gold in the team pursuit just days after placing fifth in the time trial, and the Hour Record holder will again target both events in Paris this summer.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998609862986185, \"rank\": 0.0001389514419722229, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.8167849993099696, \"rank\": 0.16983332087636926, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999695319, \"rank\": 3.042751340101416e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling, already effectively guaranteed selection for the road after his time trial bronze at last August's Glasgow Worlds, was drafted into Britain's elite track endurance programme over the winter.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 886, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9251018715259541, \"rank\": 0.08096200849176781, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}, {\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9930202493741602, \"rank\": 0.0070288099183286185, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After lining up at theCadel Evans Great Ocean Racethis weekend, he will remain in Australia for the Adelaide Track World Cup, a key stage in his tilt at double Olympic duty.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6875102945139996, \"rank\": 0.38407266234617327, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelaide\", \"score\": 0.9949029968316883, \"rank\": 0.00311014686980444, \"text\": \"Adelaide\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelaide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelaide\"}, {\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Cross-Country_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.5409607769053475, \"rank\": 0.8176600801184637, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Cross-Country_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Cross-Country_World_Cup\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His teammates Ganna and the 2016 Olympic Omnium champion Elia Viviani had the same idea, with the Italians also choosing to combine the start of their road seasons in Australia with a competitive outing on the track.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1210, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elia_Viviani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elia Viviani\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elia_Viviani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elia_Viviani\"}, {\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9998743042447609, \"rank\": 9.264960003812456e-05, \"text\": \"Italians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6875102945139996, \"rank\": 0.38407266234617327, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"European Championships: Josh Tarling dominates men's time trial in EmmenChrono des Nations: Josh Tarling beats Remco Evenepoel to secure time trial victory'His progress is amazing' - Josh Tarling the youngest Paris-Roubaix rider since 1937  \\\"Ganna's the best pursuit rider in the world and Elia's probably the best bunch rider in the world, so I could not have better company for it,\\\" Tarling toldCyclingnewsat theSurf Coast Classic, where he helped Viviani to second place behind Biniam Girmay.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9998004216481812, \"rank\": 0.0001711037580752788, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.6490003573436446, \"rank\": 0.5408310924994526, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Remco Evenepoel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\"}, {\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}, {\"begin\": 1852, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biniam_Girmay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Biniam Girmay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biniam_Girmay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biniam_Girmay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling is still a few weeks shy of his 20th birthday, but after he exceeded all expectations on the road in his debut season at WorldTour level last year, he was sounded out about the prospects of taking on a dual mandate at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tight restrictions on competing athletes at the Games means that a rider capable of combining disciplines is of immense value, and Tarling has pedigree on the boards.\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He claimed European titles at junior and under-23 level, and he collected enough points on the track in Geneva and Grenchen over the winter to qualify for the World Cup.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geneva\", \"score\": 0.9999999908459358, \"rank\": 8.997098917362529e-09, \"text\": \"Geneva\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geneva\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geneva\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It depends on how it goes, but ideally I'd like to do the team pursuit and maybe the Madison at the Olympics,\\\" Tarling said.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have qualified for the World Cup here, just after Cadel's, so I will do that and see how it goes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond Adelaide, Tarling - like Ganna and Viviani - is unlikely to race on the track again until the summer, with his Ineos duties taking precedence.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2902, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You only have to do one World Cup, so it'll be just training, I think,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, if the track team needs me I will do it, but it's mainly just training for the track and fitting it in around the road racing.\\\"\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling enjoyed a fine debut season at Ineos in 2023, testing the waters at a number of WorldTour events and turning heads against the watch.\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3196, \"end\": 3201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as taking bronze behind Ganna and Remco Evenepoel at the Worlds, he won the European time trial title, the Chrono des Nations and a stage of the Renewi Tour.\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3341, \"end\": 3356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Remco Evenepoel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\"}, {\"begin\": 3414, \"end\": 3432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrono_des_Nations\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6684696504670273e-28, \"text\": \"Chrono des Nations\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrono_des_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chrono_des_Nations\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last year went really well and I can go into more races now with confidence that I can actually do something in them.\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know there is room to improve,\\\" Tarling said.\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This year I can be a good helper, I understand the bunch really well, and I can have my opportunities when they come in time trials and maybe a road stage at some point.\\\"\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Australia this month, Tarling has largely been deployed in a supporting role in the service of Viviani and Jhonatan Narv\\u00e1ez, though he politely downplayed the idea that he was biding his time ahead of his own chance to shine later in the campaign.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 4057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3810, \"end\": 3819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6875102945139996, \"rank\": 0.38407266234617327, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest, I do not mind leading out and things like that,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not see it as 'opportunities,' I just see it as different roles.\\\"\", \"from\": 4132, \"to\": 4203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even so, taking on two different roles in Paris is an opportunity to be seized.\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4247, \"end\": 4252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999695319, \"rank\": 3.042751340101416e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone is a degree-qualified journalist that has accumulated decades of wide-ranging experience while working across a variety of leading media organisations.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She joinedCyclingnewsas a Production Editor at the start of the 2021 season and has now moved into the role of Australia Editor.\", \"from\": 4445, \"to\": 4573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4556, \"end\": 4565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6875102945139996, \"rank\": 0.38407266234617327, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously she worked as a freelance writer, Australian Editor atElla CyclingTipsand as a correspondent forReutersandBloomberg.\", \"from\": 4574, \"to\": 4701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cycling was initially purely a leisure pursuit for Simone, who started out as a business journalist, but in 2015 her career focus also shifted to the sport.\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4858, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cyclingnews is part of Future plc, an international media group and leading digital publisher.Visit our corporate site.\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 4979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4860, \"end\": 4871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cyclingnews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\"}, {\"begin\": 4883, \"end\": 4893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Future plc\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 Future Publishing Limited Quay House, The Ambury, Bath BA1 1UA.\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 5046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4983, \"end\": 5000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.316306570893141e-20, \"text\": \"Future Publishing\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\"}, {\"begin\": 5014, \"end\": 5019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9999986630414084, \"rank\": 9.60511830083588e-07, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"England and Wales company registration number 2008885.\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5068, \"end\": 5075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7504604